mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "Square Dance Date Book", "On the Record and Record Report", "From the Floor", "As I See It", "Square Dancing in Industry", "The Dancer's Walkthru", "Charm As It Applies to Square Dancing", "Americana: This Little Old Sod Shanty", "Style Series: Variations For All Four", "Personal Portrait: Harriette Blohm", "'Round the Outside Ring", "Workshop", "The Caller of the Month: Ed Epperson", "A Look at Round Dancing", "Paging the Roundancers: Gene and Ima Baylis", and "Experimental Lab - Hoop De Doo".
